A '''jakka seed''' was a type of small [[Seed/Legends|seed]]. The [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Darsha Assant]] once mentally noted that an individual [[Force-sensitive/Legends|connected]] to [[The Force/Legends|the Force]] could [[Force sense/Legends|detect]] the presence of a [[Species/Legends|life-form]] even if its [[Brain/Legends|brain]] was the size of a jakka seed.<ref name="DM:SH">''[[Darth Maul: Shadow Hunter]]''</ref>

